    "summary": "We consider this governance action to be constitutional.",
    "rationaleStatement": "This proposal is an Info Action concerning the Net Change Limit required under Article 2, Section 7 of the Cardano Constitution, and no clear violation is observed. Therefore, this proposal is deemed constitutional.",
